  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Basal ganglia are involved in the control of motor, cognitive and emotional behaviours. The
      aim of this study is to precisely evaluate patients with basal ganglia focal lesions both
      with or without loss of psychic-self activation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
